Co-workers
-> Concept used for parallel execution.
-> Parrallel execution means running multiple testcases on same time
-> Advantage of workers : fast execution and time saving
Alert
->Simple alert
->Confirmation alert
->Prompt alert
Visual Testing
-> used to identify UI changes
-> Visual testing will detect font change issues, color change issues, alignment issues, layout issues, space issues,missing or extra elements, pixel changes etc.
-> How it works:
* First run: Playwright takes a screenshot and saves it as the “baseline” / golden image.
* Every run after: Takes a new screenshot and pixel-compares it to the baseline.
* If pixels differ: Test fails and Playwright gives you a diff image showing what changed.
-> API Testing
PUT- Complete updation
PATCH- Partial update
GET
POST
DELETE
Status code for GET-200
Status code for POST-201
Status code for server error- 500
Status code for bad request-400
Status code for page not found-404

